com.isoterik.mgdx.input

Class KeyCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.Input.Keys
      • com.isoterik.mgdx.input.KeyCodes

  • public final class KeyCodes
extends com.badlogic.gdx.Input.Keys
    Provides the key codes of all keys supported by libGDX. There is no major difference between it and Input.Keys. This makes it more beginner friendly compared to the alternative.
